{"tid":1364162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班連登仔破壞經濟","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:01:06.000Z","uid":260428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8693fa6817df7baa6334b2f6fb4bb6b312fe23b","tid":1364162,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:51:58.000Z","msg":"宜家人人都唔敢黎香港<br />\n最受影響喺旅行，零售，地產！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">你地咁搞落去，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我仲點收貴租開金鋪藥房吖！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲諗住亂洗香港啲錢，<br />\n呃你地整新產業，<br />\n唔整化淡廠，<br />\n控制新聞<br />\n迫你靠中共！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班連登仔壞我好事<br />\n<br />\n信唔信我叫人著白杉<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">整個林鄭追悼會<br />\n我相信佢死咗，一定有人份緊佢做特首！唔喺點會做得咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"72db4871b9144ebb6056e9772f0bbda72058cd4d","tid":1364162,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"[727] 元朗好去處<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364076</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"513390f4875278348ea7d47e5f535732b41badf7","tid":1364162,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fEbP0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fEbP0C.jpg&h=c0319962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李鵬未死咖！<br />\n咪信TVB，專出假新聞<br />\n死左果位，應該是林鄭，<br />\n唔喺林鄭就喺李家起之類"},{"pid":"ec99057ff428fc02b28e20c09b83a21d86847be6","tid":1364162,"uid":107216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"香港人好快買得起<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">27/7元朗見</span></span>"},{"pid":"d34ec5a63b74097d8f03b2e82eb36e7a4fb596b4","tid":1364162,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"悼念喺咪叫佢落地獄咁解"}]}